title: People Pleaser
description: Blossom neglects her promise to Bubbles when she takes on too many things leaving Buttercup and Bubbles to fend for themselves.

title: Por unos Duncans mas
description: Mientras trataba de fotocopiar su trasero en la nueva y elegante fotocopiadora del Chef, Duncan accidentalmente hace otro Duncan completo. iExcelente! Este otro Duncan puede hacer todas las cosas de la escuela mientras el verdadero Duncan se enfría. Pero las cosas van mal cuando el otro Duncan decide copiarse a sí mismo para poder relajarse también.

title: Ain't That a Kick in the Side?
description: After Witch Way teases Prohyas by calling him, "Vambre's sidekick," Prohyas intensifies his efforts to prove them wrong.

title: Captain Bamboozle
description: Mr. Mxyzptlk decides to create some mischief by endowing Shazam's well-meaning Uncle Dudley with superpowers bigger than anyone in the league.

title: Goodbye and Good Riddance
description: Summer's over and Ben is back at school. Unable to tell anyone that's he all these cool aliens that they've heard about all summer, Ben suddenly realizes he's gone from a "hero" to a "zero", that is until Vilgax comes after him with a vengeance. Ben must now reveal his hero side to his parents and to his fellow classmates. In doing so he saves his town and teams up with his dad to destroy Vilgax once and for all. But there is some bad news...Gwen has switched schools and is in Ben's class!

title: My Fair Carol
description: KO, Enid and Rad team up to help Carol out with a special occasion.

title: Drawn to Sports with Hannah
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Hannah competes in track and field.

title: Stolen Retriever
description: When Vic cooks up a scheme to "borrow" people's dogs and return them for reward money, he gets in over his head with disastrous results!

title: Paint Me a Picture!
description: Pocoyo has decided to paint a portrait. But none of his friends will sit still long enough for him to be able to finish his picture. Pocoyo is sad because he feels like he hasn't managed to do what he set out to do - but looking at his picture with fresh eyes he sees that his picture really does capture the true essence of his friends.

title: The Schooling
description: Gumball and Darwin are at the convenience store considering playing truant. Larry warns them that if they don't take their education seriously they'll end up like him. To prove his point, Larry lets Gumball and Darwin work some of his many roles to make them appreciate the value of a good education.

title: Trabajando en Equipo
description: El Sr. Gar trae a un equipo de expertos en construcción para que ayuden a K.O., Enid y Rad.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Memory Foam
description: When a new mattress sucks away all of Pizza Steve's memories, Uncle Grandpa and the crew must find a way to get them back.

title: Historias de miedo
description: Durante la fiesta de Halloween de la banda, iUnikitty descubre que Rick no le teme a nada! Para contagiarle el espíritu festivo, Unikitty cuenta sus propias ideas de lo que es una historia espeluznante, con la esperanza de asustar al inconmovible de Rick por una vez. iPero cada cuento es aún más espeluznante (y más tonto) que el anterior!

title: La Formula de Manzana
description: Manzana necesita encontrar una fórmula divertida que le permita conseguir un papel cómico en una película.

title: Los Supervillanso se Unen
description: Después de una pausa en las payasadas alienígenas, un inquieto Ben les sugiere a Max y Gwen que podría ser un mejor héroe si fuera solo. Pero cuando Vilgax consigue la ayuda de Zombozo para construir un mecanismo hipnotizador gigante para hipnotizar al mundo entero, Ben debe replantearse su estrategia si quiere derrotar al equipo de supervillanos.

title: The Future is Cardboard
description: The kids meet an eccentric Cardboard Creator that invites Craig to help finish his masterpiece.

title: Cellie
description: Fed up with sharing, Panda forbids his brothers from using his cellphone any longer. But when the brothers get their own super advanced smartphones, Panda starts to succumb to crippling jealousy.

title: Fashion Bears
description: In order to abide by the clothing policy of their favorite Boba shop, the Bears get some new outfits. But with new looks come new lives including office work, fashion modeling and even falling in love!

title: Caillou and the Big Slide/Caillou the Sailor/Caillou and the Creepy Crawlies
description: The playschool is going swimming, and it's Caillou's very first time on a water slide./Mommy and Daddy are going out to a party and Caillou is excited to hear that Grandpa is coming to babysit./Rosie doesn't like bugs - she thinks they're icky!

title: Professor Proofed
description: After the Professor's latest experiment goes awry, the girls become overprotective.

title: The Space Beam
description: The new rulers of Plun-Darr say they'll bring one of the Mutants home; whichever one of them activates a homing beacon that will blow up the Thundercats. Now it's every Mutant for themselves as they battle it out to be the one to activate the beacon!

title: ThunderDogs
description: The Thundercats agree to foster a demonic puppy from the Astral Plane until they can find it the perfect owner. But could the perfect owner be their worst enemy? Their worst enemy is Mumm-Ra in case you forgot!

title: La Invitacion
description: Craig y sus amigos están invitados a una exclusiva merienda con deliciosos postres, si es que pueden quedarse hasta el final de la fiesta.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Where's Flop?
description: It's lunchtime! Bing's hungry for carrots. But what happens when Flop pops to the shops and Bing stays at home with Amma and Sula?

title: #MisgivingTree
description: Jessica Cruz and Pam Isley bond over protecting an ancient tree from being cut down. Neither of them realizes who the other's alter ego is, or the lengths to which they'll go to protect what's important.

title: Cartoon Feud
description: Control Freak forces the Titans and the Scooby Gang to compete on Family Feud.

title: The Beepers: The Visitor
description: The Beepers find the perfect groove after a new friend shreds a little too hard.

title: Fire Maker
description: The Ice Emperor learns of the ninja's arrival and sends his Blizzard Samurai warriors to destroy them and the villagers who sheltered them.

title: Hostile Take Over/The Big Bounce
description: Hostile Take Over: After more unsuccessful attempts to harness Core Cell energy the AO must battle their own Bakugan with AAAnimus tech in order to save them./The Big Bounce: The AO confront Philomena with concerns about her control over the Core Cell energy and are fired in the most unceremonious of manners.

title: So Long, and Thanks for All the Smoothies
description: When Ben and Rook investigate a mysterious alien ghost ship, they discover that Argit and the Vreedle Brothers are fighting for possession of a doomsday device! (Introducing Solid Plugg.)

title: Wide Load Vacay: Dumbrella
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, have been traveling on the back of a truck in the rain for days. Charlie produces an umbrella to help his friend but unfortunately it's a "dumbrella" and it's looking to have some fun with them!

title: La Fe
description: Alan perdió su fe en la humanidad y puso el mundo blanco y negro. Gumball tiene que superar el odio que siente hacia Alan para recuperar el color a través del canto.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: New Bro on Campus
description: High School Muscle Man wants to prove he's cooler than the new kid on campus.

title: Un Gran Enfrentamiento
description: Lightning por fin revela la ubicación de la Célula Núcleo, pero cuando Los Fantásticos llegan, descubren que Magnus fue más rápido que ellos.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Love Songs
description: The Titans follow their heart with songs devoted to their greatest relationships: Beast Boy & Raven, Cyborg & Jinx and the Titans & Food.

title: Gryffindor v Hufflepuff
description: Dame Helen Mirren hosts the first episode of this epic TV event series. Over 4 episodes the Houses of Hogwarts will do battle to see which team knows the most about the wizarding world, featuring celebrity guests, actors from the original films and more Harry Potter Magic than you could find on a day trip to Diagon Alley. Tonight's match up sees the brave Gryffindors face the loyal Hufflepuffs for a guaranteed place in the grand finale.
originalseriesname: Harry Potter: Hogwarts Tournament of Houses

title: Just Wait in the Car
description: As Mary runs errands, Clarence waits in the car and struggles to fight boredom.

title: Fixing a Flonk
description: Wanting to stop Flonk from being an evildoer for good, Prohyas tries to find Flonk a permanent venue for his nasty comedy. Vambre, however, wants to deliver him to the cops as usual.

title: Pleito animado
description: Control Fenómeno obliga a los Titanes y a la Scooby-pandilla a competir en Pleito Familiar.

title: The Truth Stinks
description: Badgerclops smells, but Mao Mao and Adorabat don't know how to tell him.

title: El Hacedor de Fuego
description: El Emperador de Hielo se entera de la llegada de los ninjas y envía a sus guerreros Samurais Blizzard a destruirlos, y a todos los aldeanos que los albergaron.

title: Makes Zen to Me/Say Uncle
description: Makes Zen to Me: When Buttercup gets a fortune cookie saying peace lies within, the most violent of Powerpuffs sets out on a quest for inner peace./Say Uncle: The girls' go to pick up the Professor's brother at the train station, but mistake him for a wild-man being transported to the circus.

title: Clayton
description: Darwin needs to find a photo of Clayton to put on the cover of the school yearbook - but he makes the mistake of seeking help from Tobias, who has his eye on the cover spot himself! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: The Brood
description: Craig's determination to get his granddad a cicada shell causes him, Kelsey and JP to become trapped in their stump!

title: Veamos el Show de Boxmore
description: Nuestros héroes descubren que las grabaciones de la cámara de seguridad de Boxmore son la cosa más divertida del mundo.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Meet Cheetara
description: Cheetara is the coolest cat around! Not only is she so fast that she can outrun lightning, but so clever she can outsmart Mumm-Ra's evil plans! Villains don't stand a chance against Cheetara…well, unless Mumm-Ra uses his Doom Staff, then she might be in trouble.

title: Nuggets de Pollo de Sabiduria
description: Cuando Ben y Max comienzan a discutir, Ben se convierte en Fuego para desahogarse, contra la voluntad de Max. Pero una vez que el Dr. Animo lo ve y convierte a Max en un pollo, Ben debe enmendar su error si quiere salvar a su Abuelo y detener al Dr. Animo.

title: Fleas Help Me
description: Uncle Grandpa and the gang help their K9 pal, Charlie Burgers, get rid of his flea infestation.

title: Top of the Titans:  Raddest Songs
description: From "Booty Scooty" to "Sour Grapes" to "The Night Begins to Shine," Birdarang is here to count down the raddest music from Teen Titans Go!

title: Drawn to Change
description: Cartoon Network is Drawn to Change, and Craig of the Creek talks to Martin Luther King Junior's granddaughter Yolanda about how kids can change the world!

title: Lunchbox
description: It's lunchtime! Bing shows Pando and Sula his brand new Hoppity Voosh lunchbox! And Pando has the exact same one MATCH! But then they mix their lunchboxes up.

title: Despedidos
description: Los Fantásticos confrontan a Filomena, preocupados de que ella controle la energía de la Célula núcleo, y son despedidos de una forma poco profesional.

title: For a Few Duncans More
description: While trying to photocopy his butt on Chef's fancy new copier Duncan accidentally makes an entire other Duncan. Great! This other Duncan can do all the school stuff while the real Duncan chills. But things go badly when the other Duncan decides to copy himself so he can chill too.

title: The Wild Hunt
description: A fierce creature is terrorizing the Candy Kingdom but before Finn can slay the beast, he must first overcome a guilty conscience.

title: Snow Month
description: After a snow day saves Blossom from having to face a boy who's asked her out, she decides to use her ice breath to keep it going even if that means plunging Townsville into eternal winter complete with monstrous yetis!

title: Voleibol
description: Steven está decidido a ayudar a la Perla original de Diamante Rosa para sanar la cicatriz en su rostro.

title: #AbracadabraPalooza
description: En un intento por hacer que Karen se sienta mejor con un granito que le salió, Zee le cuenta la avergonzante transición que le dio poderes mágicos y la grieta que eso generó entre ella y su padre.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Top of the Titans: Beast Boy & Cyborg Songs
description: Birdarang counts down the best musical moments from the raddest bros you know, Beast Boy and Cyborg. Waffles!

title: Teen Titans Vroom
description: Teen Titans Vroom: Part 1: In this episode of "Turbo Titans Go Force" the Titans gain the ability to transform into cars. /Teen Titans Vroom: Part 2: In the exciting conclusion of "Turbo Titans Go Force" the Titans must learn to work together to stop Dr. Military.

title: Meet Lion-O
description: Meet Lion-O and the Thundercats! After fleeing their home planet, the Thundercats find themselves stranded on Third Earth where they face the evil Mumm-Ra. But Lion-O is strong! He's tough! There's nothing he can't do! Except maybe open really big jars of cookies…

title: #GothamCon
description: A fun day for Barbara Gordon and her bestie Harleen Quinzel (at Gotham City's annual geekfest, the Annual Convention of Gotham City Enthusiats!) is turned on its head when, out of nowhere, the villainous Harley Quinn shows up to wreak havoc! Lucky for everyone, Batgirl just happens to be in the area...

title: Forever Ever
description: When Vic and Val do a sloppy job cleaning up in Maria Theresa's attic, they accidentally set off a time loop, trapping them in an endless series of chores forever! They must figure out how to stop the loop and return time back to normal.

title: Changeable Terraingable
description: Personality conflicts between Vambre and Prohyas come to a head as the Warriors miraculously manage to ace a mission at an ever changing labyrinth.

title: #ElShowDeLasBestias
description: Cuando Babs y Kara discuten sobre cual de sus perros es mejor, deciden resolver la situación en el concurso anual de perros de Metrópolis, donde Ace, el Bati-sabueso y Krypto, el Superperro, deberán salvar el día.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: The Powerpuff Girls: A Documentary/Girls Gone Mild
description: The Powerpuff Girls a Documentary: A film student attempts to do a documentary on the Powerpuff Girls and learns catching these superheroes at rest is harder than he thought./Girls Gone Mild: When Parents Against Powerpuffs tell the girls that their superheroics are becoming too imitable, the girls must hold back on fighting crime.

title: Weapon of Choice
description: Worried that his sword is a glorified consolation prize, Mao Mao sets out to prove the worth of his weapon.

title: Vambre's Guilty Pleasure
description: Vambre tries her best to keep her tough Warrior reputation intact and still go to the cutesy wootsy Piggiepie Jones stage show.

title: Follow Your Dreams
description: Apple and Onion need to find a dream to follow, so that their lives don't head nowhere.

title: Lego DC Super Hero Girls: Brain Drain
description: Missing memories provide an intriguing mystery for everyone's favorite young female heroes in this all-new animated film.  When Supergirl, Wonder Woman, Batgirl, Harley Quinn, Bumblebee, Poison Ivy and Katana suddenly realize they cannot remember a single moment from their Monday at Super Hero High, the young Super Heroes spring into sleuthing action! Suspecting foul-play, they band together to retrace their steps and uncover the mystery of who exactly stole their memories - and, what nefarious plan might be afoot?

title: Point to the Plaza
description: When a Gloop infestation takes over the plaza, Point arrives to contain the situation.

title: Drawn to Sports with Luke
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Luke is passionate about running, jumping and climbing in Ninja Racing.

title: What a Stinker
description: Chep is very excited: tonight, a rare and extremely stinky plant is going to bloom! But he already promised Mush-Mush to play their favourite game. When he chooses the flower instead, Mush-Mush is angry and the two friends stop talking. But when Mush-Mush realises that Chep is about to miss the blooming, he decides he won't let that happen and helps his friend!

title: El Mensaje
description: Lloyd y su compañero lobo encuentran una cueva y encuentran al Mech adentro. Escuchan un mensaje de Zane que les da una pista de su destino.

title: Apointa a la Plaza
description: Cuando la plaza se infesta de pegote, P.O.I.N.T. llega para contener la situación.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: #LaConvencionDeGotham
description: Un divertido día para Barbara Gordon y su mejor amiga Harley Quinzel en la Convención Anual de Gotham City, es puesto cabeza abajo cuando, de la nada, ila malvada Harley Quinn aparece para sembrar el caos! Por suerte para todos, Batgirl se encuentra casualmente en el área...
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: #Abracadabrapalooza
description: In an attempt to make Karen feel better about a pimple, Zee recounts her embarrassing transition into magichood, and the rift it created between her and her father.

title: Silent Treatment/Sweet "n" Sour
description: The Silent Treatment: When the girls go to see a silent movie with the Professor, they end up getting pulled into the film by an old-time villain./Sweet 'n' Sour: The girls must figure out how to beat Townsville's newest band of criminals: a group of adorable little animals.

title: #BeastsInShow
description: When Babs and Kara spar over whose dog is better, they decide to settle it at the Metropolis Dog Show, where Ace the Bat-Hound and Krypto the Superdog suddenly find themselves called upon to save the day… in more ways than one.

title: Espias Como Nosotros
description: El tío Andrew le advierte a Axel que su figura de acción "Agente Peligro" está prohibida, isolo para que el juguete escape solo! Axel y el equipo deben devolver a Danger al lugar que le corresponde antes de que el tío Andrew se entere.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin asks Sarah for a photo to put on the cover of the school yearbook. But when Sarah tries to help, things get a little sticky. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Top of the Titans: Dance Party!
description: Come correct because it's a Titans Dance Battle! Birdarang reviews the greatest dance songs in Teen Titans Go! history.

title: All Koiled Up
description: When Ben grows impatient with the snail like pace of gardening, he goes O-E Overflow to pick up the pace and accidentally floods the community garden, but once a giant sink hole appears and frees King Koil and his Kimodo Dragon from below, Ben must quickly right his wrong and capture the baddies if he is to save the coastal city of Bayburgh.

title: Elly's Doll
description: Pocoyo is charged with looking after Elly's favorite doll, but he breaks it. Instead of telling her the truth, he pretends to be the doll. It's only when nature gets the better of Pocoyo that Elly realizes what's going on. She forgives Pocoyo warmly and mends her doll.

title: Oportunidades Laborales
description: Después de derrotar a Magnus, los Fantásticos reciben una oferta de empleo de alguien inesperado... Filomena Dusk.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Big City Dancers
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, traveling on the back of a truck visit NYC where the rhythms of the city make Charlie wanna dance his little back porch off. Frank … not so much. But when you go far enough into the city, anything can happen.

title: Teachers
description: When Darwin asks his friends which teacher deserves to be on the yearbook cover, they struggle to find a single worthy candidate! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Drawn To Expression!
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating queer youth and families in the LGBTQIA+ community that radiate joy, pride, and inclusivity. We are championing the ways these kids and families form connections to their authentic selves by expressing their creativity and queer identity through their art.

title: Pokin and Proddin
description: Valentino wins a coveted internship to work in the Tez administration. Initially intending to use his insider status to spy on Tez, Val unexpectedly finds himself enjoying the comradery of office life.

title: Ranger Tabes
description: To recover a missing package, the Bears get help from Ranger Tabes, an eccentric forest ranger. But her overblown sense of justice might be too much for the Bears to handle.

title: Return of Thermometron 9000
description: During a brutal heatwave, Axel and his team must track down Thermometron 9000, stolen by Ice Crusher for two purposes - to keep his hockey rink from melting and to bait the good toys into a rematch!

title: Son of Rap Bear
description: When Flame Princess is coaxed into a high stakes battle against the indomitable Son of Rap Bear, Finn must help her search for a new strategy.

title: La Camada
description: La determinación de Craig de conseguirle a su abuelo un caparazón de cigarra hace que él, Kelsey y JP queden atrapados en su tronco.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: We Baby Bears: BHA Bha Song
description: We Baby Bears follows baby bear brothers Grizz, Panda, and Ice Bear as they journey in a magical box to fantastic different worlds in search of their perfect home.

title: Missing Cat
description: When Chelsea accidentally lets her pet cat Crumbles out, the cat goes missing! Reluctant to ask for help, she struggles to find the cat before anyone realizes it's gone. It's up to cat whisperer Clarence to interject and find Crumbles, whether Chelsea wants his help or not!

title: Alan
description: Darwin wants to put Alan on the cover of the school yearbook - but Alan's apparent modesty gets in the way. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Nido de buitres
description: Craig y sus amigos forman una banda, pero a Craig lo atormenta una pesadilla aterradora.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Go!
description: Robin struggles to lead the Titans after finding out that his catchphrase "GO!" is trademarked by another team.

title: Tea & Basketball
description: Sylvester wants to play tea with the girls while Lola wants to play basketball with the boys.

title: Meet Tanya Keys
description: When bounty hunter Tanya Keys comes to town for Badgerclops, it's up to Mao Mao and Adorabat to save their friend -- even if he's been on the wrong side of the law.

title: Banda de por Vida
description: Cuando Vic y Val acompañan a Xochi a un concierto punk, quieren demostrar que son lo suficientemente geniales para salir con ella. Pero en un intento desesperado por tener onda, terminan arruinando el concierto.

title: Tez dice
description: Vic y Val están impresionados con el nuevo mago de la ciudad, pero las cosas se complican cuando aceptan ayudarlo con un nuevo truco, a pesar de los deseos de Chata.

title: River of Gold
description: Apple and Onion find a mysterious book but they better read it fast before it disappears forever.

title: The Beepers: Funky Time
description: The Beepers play with tempo and learn that adapting to change can be…sweaty.

title: Inadvertant Inversion
description: As Elliott, Mo and Frankie all try something new at the Hive, they find their worlds are about to be turned upside down again.

title: El Amo
description: Los Watterson juegan un juego de rol fantástico para resolver sus diferencias.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: The Return of Aunt Grandma
description: Aunt Grandma is back and still bent on ruining Uncle Grandpa.

title: The Buddy
description: Anais and school psycho Jamie are accused of the same techno-crime. They are forced to team up to discover the real culprit in order to prove their innocence. After solving the case, they realize that they have more in common than they thought...

title: Un Experimento Fallido
description: El plan de Filomena Dusk para redireccionar la energía de la Célula Núcleo fracasa, y Los Fantásticos deben pelear contra sus propios compañeros de trabajo dentro de las instalaciones de AAAnimus.

title: Lista de Traviesos
description: Es Nochebuena y Brock está emocionado por la visita de Santa Claus. Mientras se prepara para que Master Frown le lea un cuento para dormir, Unikitty y la banda irrumpen en su casa. Están ahí para evitar que Master Frown arruine más Navidades. Frown se declara inocente, pero Unikitty y la banda cuentan las historias de las Navidades pasadas que ya arruinó. ¿Frown probará su inocencia o se pondrá a la cabeza de la lista de los traviesos?

title: We Baby Bears Official Trailer: New Series
description: These baby bears are searching for a brand new home, and they're off to fantastical worlds and new adventures along the way. Watch the official trailer for We Baby Bears, the brand new show from the creators of We Bare Bears, coming to Cartoon Network in 2022.

title: Alpha Bodies
description: Cartoonito presents Alpha Bodies! It's time to use our bodies to make every letter of the alphabet, from A to Z, but one over-eager letter keeps getting ahead of itself.

title: Lift With Your Back
description: Rigby wants to prove to Mordecai that he can earn a paycheck from another job.

title: More
description: It's bath time! Bing's excited to do the bubbles, but how much bubble goo does Bing need?

title: Awesome vs. AAAnimus
description: Awesome V Aaanimus, Part 1: The AO plan on sneaking into AAAnimus and rescuing their Bakugan but are stopped by Benton who offers up an alternate plan./Awesome V Aaanimus, Part 2: The AO team up with Benton Dusk to recapture their stolen Bakugan and free the energy from the Mind Core Cell under the control of AAAnimus.

title: Tree
description: Bing and Pando are being diggers, planting trees in the sandpit. What will happen when Pando ruins Bing's digging?

title: Super-Villain Team-Up
description: After a lull in alien antics, a restless Ben suggests to Max and Gwen that he might be a better hero if he went solo, but once Vilgax enlists the help of Zombozo to build a giant hypno-mechanism to hypnotize the entire world, Ben must rethink his strategy if he is to defeat the super-villain team-up.

title: Banana Joe
description: When Principal Brown sets Darwin the task of making the school yearbook, Darwin starts by asking class clown Banana Joe for a simple selfie to put on the cover. But with Banana Joe, things are never that simple. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Monster Reunion
description: Steven reunites with an old friend.

title: Just Like Robots
description: Axel and the team find themselves bested by Madcap when the baddie uses their digital devices to track their every move in combat, forcing our heroes to act unpredictably.

title: Of Predators and Prey Part 2
description: While trapped in Khyber's ship, Ben learns details about the origin of the Nemetrix, and the link between Khyber, Malware, and Dr. Psychobos! (Introducing new Nemetrix alien Tyrannopede.)

title: Azulejo
description: Steven cuestiona los motivos de una misteriosa fusión que de repente se presenta en su casa.

title: Drawn to Sports with Olivia
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Olivia is a tennis player who is also passionate about art.

title: High Flying Hostiles/Backfire Brawl
description: High Flying Hostiles: While escorting the Mind Core Cell to AAAnimus Campus, the AO are attacked by Masato Kazami and his Body Guards./Backfire Brawl: Philomena's attempt to refocus the Mind Core Cell's power backfires and the AO must fight their fellow employees inside the AAAnimus Campus.

title: Green with Envy
description: When the local news interviews Uncle Andrew about his toy inventing, an envious Galileo stages a play in the park with the help of Axel and the team, only to be interrupted by an equally envious Madcap - out to steal the spotlight for himself!

title: Mision Espacial Peligrosa
description: Después de la explosión de su nave espacial, Unikitty y la banda flotan indefensos por el espacio. Mientras tratan de formular un plan que los lleve a casa a salvo, vuelven a ver qué parte de la responsabilidad por la destrucción de su nave tiene cada uno. ¿Lograrán volver a casa? Y lo que es más importante, ¿quién tendrá la culpa si no lo hacen?

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Super Hero High
description: Supergirl arrives at Super Hero High and struggles to learn to control her new powers. Meanwhile, the Junior Detective Club investigates a mysterious rash of security breaches centered around the teleportation Boom Tubes.

title: Dissing Cousins
description: It's International Cousins Day and Owen and Gwen are dreading the fact that their cousins Max and Ella are spending the day with them. And soon everyone else will understand why.

title: He Who Wears the Clown
description: After trying on the nose of a clown Owen learns that this is how clowns are made and he is stuck as a clown until he can trick someone else into asking to try on the nose.

title: Alone at Sea
description: Steven and Greg take a boat trip out to sea and find themselves in dangerous water.

title: Inodoro Real
description: Cuando los otros chicos temen que Harold se haya descargado a sí mismo por accidente en el elegante inodoro nuevo de Chef, viajan al desagüe a rescatarlo. Pero, ¿encontrarán a Harold antes que el mítico Cocodrilo Rey los deje atrapados bajo tierra para siempre?

title: Senor Casero
description: El propietario amenazó a Master Frown y a Brock con desalojarlos a menos que arreglen el daño que le hicieron a su apartamento. Preocupado, Brock invita a Unikitty y a la pandilla para que los ayuden. En lugar de hacer lo que los chicos quieren en su casa, Unikitty procede a hacer lo que ella quiere. Al darse cuenta de su error, devuelve el apartamento a su antiguo estado asqueroso, pero ahora Frown y Brock están en peligro de desalojo de nuevo. Deben aliarse a Unikitty y la banda para luchar contra el malvado casero y salvar su hogar.

title: Arma de Eleccion
description: Preocupado de que su espada sea un premio consuelo con pretensiones, Mao Mao decide salir a demostrar el valor de su arma.

title: Todo Enrollado
description: Cuando Ben se impacienta con el ritmo lento de la jardinería, se convierte en O-E Overflow para acelerar las cosas y, por accidente, inunda el jardín de la comunidad.

title: Rio de Oro
description: Manzana y Cebolla intentan terminar un cuento antes de que el libro desaparezca para siempre.

title: Bajo el Puente
description: Craig y sus amigos viajan para encontrar madreselva en el arroyo, pero descubren una parte completamente nueva del arroyo.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Keen on Keane/Not So Awesome Blossom
description: Keen on Keane: It's Valentine's Day and the girls notice that Ms. Keane is all alone. Time for a little matchmaking, but who will be the lucky fella?/Not So Awesome Blossom: When Blossom's attack plans fail one after the other, she loses confidence in herself as the group's leader.

title: King Koil
description: Ben and Gwen spend the day volunteering at Repto Ranch and come face to face with King Koil, but need to quickly overcome their fear of snakes if they are to rescue the released critters and defeat the slithery baddie.

title: Eternamente
description: Cuando Vic y Val limpian el ático de María Teresa a medias, ipor accidente inician un bucle de tiempo que los atrapa en una serie interminable de tareas eternas! Ahora deben averiguar cómo detener el bucle y devolver el tiempo a la normalidad.

title: The Faith
description: Everything in Elmore is suddenly just various shades of grey, and things all over town are going wrong. Gumball and Darwin follow the mayhem and learn that one person was holding the whole town together: Alan. They have to restore his faith in the world to bring color back to Elmore.

title: Sigue Tus Suenos
description: Manzana y Cebollín necesitan encontrar un sueño que perseguir para que sus vidas tengan un rumbo.

title: Seventeen
description: A mysterious knight crashes Finn's birthday bash and presents him with a dangerous gift.

title: Band For Life
description: When Vic and Val tag along with Xochi to a punk concert, they want to prove that they're cool enough to hang out with her. But in a desperate attempt to be cool, they wind up destroying the concert.

title: Ghost Camp
description: When Lucas and friends go camping, Avocado tells a scary story. Lucas now thinks there's a ghost in the garden.

title: El futuro es de Carton
description: Los niños conocen a un excéntrico Creador de Cartón que invita a Craig a ayudarlo a terminar su obra maestra.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Perdiendo el Control
description: Después de más intentos fallidos por aprovechar la energía la Célula núcleo, Los Fantásticos deben pelear contra sus propios Bakugan usando tecnología AAAnimus para salvarlos.

title: The So-Bad-Ical
description: When a new substitute shows up, KO and Dendy decide they need to get their old teacher back.

title: #IlusionesDeGrandeza
description: Lista para salir de la sombra de su padre, Zatara busca la fama y el reconocimiento con una presentación para su propia audiencia en el muelle. Pero cuando su acto es tildado de fraude, ella pierde el control y accidentalmente libera terribles seres que causan estragos en el muelle.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: El Peor Ninja de Todos
description: De regreso en ciudad Ninjago, tres criminales se enteran de la ausencia de los ninjas y organizan una fuga de la prisión Kryptarium, contando historias sobre cómo fueron capturados mientras avanzaban.

title: Big Trouble Little Babies
description: When they realize they're too small for the rides at an amusement park, the Bears use a magic potion to get bigger.

title: Daddy Issues
description: C.J. wants to win a "cut the Cheeser's" card at a mini-golf tournament.

title: The Tiger Train
description: When Yong Bao visits Sodor, a jealous Thomas sets out to prove he's the braver train and challenges Yong Bao to a series of bravery challenges, only to have his plan backfire.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Conozcan a Tanya Keys
description: Cuando Tanya Keys, la cazadora de recompensas, llega a la ciudad para atrapar a Colosal, Mao Mao y Adorabat son los encargados de salvar a su amigo... aunque se haya metido en asuntos ilegales.

title: Chicken Nuggets of Wisdom
description: When Ben and Max get into an argument, Ben goes Heatblast to blow off steam against Max's wishes; but once Dr. Animo spots him and subsequently turns Max into a chicken, it's up to Ben to right his wrong if he is to save his Grandpa and stop Dr. Animo.

title: Top of the Naughty List
description: It's Christmas Eve and Brock is excited for Santa to come and visit as he settles down for a bedtime story from Master Frown, Unikitty and gang burst in. They are there to stop Master Frown from ruining any more Christmases. Frown pleads innocent but Unikitty and the gang tell the stories of the past Christmases he has already ruined.  Will Frown prove his innocence or will he rocket to the top of the Naughty List?

title: #IllusionsOfGrandeur
description: Ready to emerge from her father's shadow, Zee Zatara secretly seeks fame and acclaim performing for her own audience at the pier. But when her act is dismissed as fakery, she loses her cool and accidentally unleashes mischievous gremlins who run wild all over the pier.

title: Hello Around the World
description: Cartoonito presents Hello Around the World! All across the globe, friends greet each other in lots of different languages. Watch along and discover some of the many ways to say "Hello," around the world and beyond!

title: Messy Bessy
description: Seth must clean his room and learn to be a neater person in order to keep Messy Bessy from making his life a nightmare.

title: Maxin' and Relaxin'
description: Mordecai wants to get a mix tape from his parents' house.

title: The Beepers: Spotlight
description: When a spotlight gives everyone a chance to solo, a shy Beeper discovers the courage to shine.

title: The Throw Down/Brawl for It All
description: The Throw Down: Lightning reveals his discovery of the Mind Core Cell but the AO arrive only to discover that Magnus has already beaten them to it./Brawl for It All: With both team's Bakugan knocked into a hibernation state by the Mind Core Cell only Dan and Magnus remain locked in a brawl for it all!

title: Drawn To Rhythm: Lorenzo
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Hispanic Heritage Month with another installment of "Drawn To" that showcases kids who honor their Hispanic and Latino heritage as they are drawn to rhythm. In this piece, Lorenzo tells us about his passion for reggaetón music and soccer.

title: Tez Says
description: Vic & Val are in awe of the new magician in town, but things go awry when they agree to help him out with a new trick - despite Chata's wishes.

title: Caillou the Road Builder/Caillou's Building Adventure/A House in the Sky
description: There's been a big storm and the playschool yard is littered with branches./When Daddy and Grandpa help a charity build a new home for a needy family, Caillou comes along./Mommy and Caillou go to visit an old friend of Mom's.

title: Ben 10 vs. Negative 10 Part 1
description: Ben, Max Ben and Gwen investigate a couple of daring break-ins, only to discover they were both once secret Plumber installations. What our heroes find out is that those responsible for the break-ins are working for The Forever King. He's brought together a rogue's gallery of some of Ben's most notorious enemies to eventually steal the world's most powerful energy source...located deep inside the Plumber bunker at Mount Rushmore.

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Julian
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: Quiero Ser Payaso
description: Después de probarse la nariz de un payaso, Owen se entera de que así es como se hacen los payasos y está atrapado como un payaso hasta que puede engañar a otra persona para que le pida probarse la nariz.

title: Sparkle Magic
description: Sula is the fairy queen and shows Bing her special sparkle magic... will Bing find his own?

title: Meet Mumm-ra and the Mutants
description: The Thundercats have met their match with the evil, undead Mumm-ra! He and the bumbling Mutants have made it their goal to stop the Thundercats by any means necessary, but of course the Thundercats have other plans!

title: Salchichas y Dulce Golpe
description: Manzana y Cebollín deben superar sus obsesiones por las salchichas y los videojuegos.

title: Legend of Torbaclaun
description: When the Sweetypies think the mythical Torbaclaun has come to Pure Heart Valley, Mao Mao tries to prove to them that it isn't real.

title: Greg the Babysitter
description: Steven learns the tale of how Greg came to work at the car wash.

title: Return of the Gnomes
description: When Gus and Garth's greedy uncle makes his nephews forget the caring, sharing, and generosity they learned from the Care Bears and convinces them to return to their old selfish ways, the Bears must help them remember their caring hearts.

title: Poorbucks
description: When Morbucks loses her money, Blossom tries to reform her.

title: Landlord Lord
description: The Land Lord has threatened Master Frown and Brock with eviction unless they fix the damage they've done to their apartment. Worried, Brock invites Unikitty and the gang to help. Instead of doing what the guys want to their place, she proceeds to do what she wants. Realizing her error, she returns the apartment to its former disgusting state, but now Frown and Brock are in danger of eviction again. They must team up with Unikitty and the gang to battle the Land Lord and save their home.

title: Restaurant Wars
description: Steven must help the Frymans and the Pizzas settle a reignited rivalry between their restaurants.

title: The Message
description: Lloyd and his wolf-companion find a cave with the mech inside and a message from Zane that provides a clue to his fate.

title: The Absolute Worst!
description: Back in Ninjago City, three criminals learn of the ninja's absence and stage a breakout of Kryptarium Prison, telling tall tales of how they were captured as they go.

title: El Desfile
description: Unikitty planea un desfile para celebrar lo que cada uno tiene de único, idonde cada uno diseñará sus propias carrozas personalizadas! Pero Master Frown planea arruinar el desfile con una carroza súper deprimente. El desfile se convierte en un duelo intenso (y de una lentitud divertidísima) de coche contra carroza mientras Unikitty y los demás intentan derribar a Master Frown! ¿Le pondrá un freno Unikitty al complot a baja velocidad de Frown?

title: Bring on the Bad Guys
description: Axel, Zoe, and the team confront Madcap and his minions as they terrorize a local supermarket.

title: Big Jumping Spider
description: Lucas performs epic jumps all around House. Findley is nervous and wishes Lucas wouldn't jump.

title: What's In the Box?
description: Pocoyo's new box takes on a life of its own when Loula accidentally crawls underneath it. Eventually with the help of his friends, Pocoyo works out what's - or WHO'S - in the box.

title: It Was Them
description: Dr. Animo has escaped his Plumber prison, and Ben and Rook must track him down before he turns the world into his personal mutant ant farm! (Introducing Nemetrix alien Slamworm, Galvan Plumbers Blukic and Driba, Arctiguana, new Ben alien Crashhopper.)

title: El Reino del Jamas
description: Los ninja llegan al Never-Realm donde rápidamente se sienten abrumados. Afortunadamente, son recibidos por una tribu de pescadores de hielo que les dicen que Zane ha sido encarcelado por el malvado Emperador de hielo.

title: Cool Guy Clarence
description: When Clarence meets JT, the kid who mows their lawn, he finds a fast friend who shows him some cool new music, a new outlook on life and a sweet rat-tail! Clarence leans into the rat tail lifestyle, discovering a whole new side of Aberdale he never knew existed.

title: Mal Radical
description: Cuando llega un nuevo reemplazo, K.O. y Dendy deciden que necesitan recuperar a su antiguo profesor.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Be a Team
description: Mr. Gar brings in some team building experts to help KO, Enid and Rad.

title: The End of Muscle Man
description: The guys want to help Muscle Man finish his bucket list.

title: Mini Mongor
description: The Thunderkittens unleash a demon who is powered by fear. Too bad he's small and not that scary.

title: El Elegido
description: Tobías intenta ser el mejor amigo de Gumball.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: The Light in the Forest
description: Cheer bonds with a migrating firefly-like creature, called a Sparklewing, who stows aboard the Cloudseeker. The two become good friends, but there's a problem: Sparklewings must finish their migration to bring life-giving nutrients to the fields of the Silver Lining. Cheer's difficult and emotional parting with her new friend is only possible once they both accept that it's for a greater good.

title: Drawn to Ancestry
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Asian-American Pacific Islander Heritage Month and recognizing amazing kids who learn from their elders to pave their future! We're honoring the special bond between kids and their grandparents as they are Drawn To Ancestry.

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Ms. Opal
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: Spies Like Us
description: Uncle Andrew warns Axel that his vintage "Agent Danger" action figure is off-limits, only to have the toy escape on its own! Axel and the team must return Danger to its rightful place before Uncle Andrew finds out.

title: Hot Stretch
description: Ben and Rook encounter a race of elastic, hot-blooded aliens in Undertown who want to use a stolen nuclear fusion engine to activate a volcano! (Introducing Ester, Seebik & the Kraaho.)

title: Blenanas
description: Finn's latest literary work is met with only derision so he sets out to prove all the naysayers wrong.

title: Keeping Up with the Kryptonians
description: Mr. Mxyzptlk shows Supergirl and Superman that their innate goodness might not be so pure when he takes them to a parallel world where their counterparts are impossibly aggressive and spoiled.

title: Tygra's Garden
description: Tygra says he's done being a Thundercat after he gets engaged to a sentient flower. Now it's up to Lion-O to break up the wedding!

title: Total Eclipse of the Fart
description: After accidentally swallowing her first loose tooth and fearing that means no cash under the pillow, Leshawna tries to capture the tooth fairy. Instead, she accidentally captures the fart fairy. This comes with great consequence.

title: Sausage and Sweetie Smash
description: Onion must stop Apple from falling prey to his obsession, but a certain phone game is proving to be quite an obstacle.

title: Space Mission: Danger
description: After their spaceship explodes, Unikitty and the gang float helplessly through space. As they try to formulate a plan that will get them home safe, they flash back to how each of them is responsible for their ship being destroyed. Will they make it home, and more importantly who will be to blame if they don't.

title: Bears in the Dark
description: The Bears search for their missing box in a dark and scary cave.

title: Big Trouble in Little Aberdale
description: After stumbling upon a mysterious new kid in their neighborhood , Clarence, Jeff and Sumo decide to take the kid out on the town showing him the fun of junk food, arcades and soda! However, this new lifestyle may be more then the new kid bargained for.

title: Enemigos en el Aire
description: Cuando Los Fantásticos transportan la Célula Núcleo a las instalaciones de AAAnimus, son atacados por Masato Kazami y sus Guardaespaldas.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Eye Spy
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, are traveling on the back of a truck from Montana to Utah. Charlie wants to play a game of Eye Spy. He finds more and more obvious objects for Frank to spy but Frank isn't quite getting the hang of it. Yet!

title: Drawn To Rhythm: Jayleen
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Hispanic Heritage Month with another installment of "Drawn To" that showcases kids who honor their Hispanic and Latino heritage as they are drawn to rhythm. In this piece, Jayleen shows us some of the eight different dance styles she can do, including bachata and cumbia.

title: Musical Blocks
description: Pocoyo and Pato are having great fun playing with some magical blocks which form towers when music is played. But the fun turns to drama when Pato gets stuck on top of a high tower. How can Pocoyo return his ducky friend back to ground safely?

title: Mi Bella Carol
description: K.O., Enid y Rad se unen para ayudar a Carol para una ocasión especial.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Can I Keep It?
description: After stumbling upon a cute cat-dog-rabbit creature hybrid, or "Cadobbit," Ben ignores Grandpa Max's advice and sneaks the animal onto the Rustbucket, but is quickly in over his head as Dr. Amino's creation turns on him!

title: Bucket List
description: The Titans give Starfire a bucket list of activities to accomplish.

title: Everyone's Best/Stronger Every Day/No More Training Wheels
description: When Clementine shows up with a swimming ribbon on her chest, Caillou really wants to have one too./When a new, longer set of monkey bars is installed at the park, Caillou is disappointed./With training wheels on his bike, Caillou is having trouble keeping up with Sarah.

title: Ben 10 vs. Negative 10 Part 2
description: Ben, Max and Gwen put up an Alamo like stand inside the bunker at Mount Rushmore and against great odds take down the Forever King's band of baddies. In the end, Ben goes Upchuck and digests the powerful energy source, preventing the Forever King from using it for nefarious purposes. However this ultimate baddie is able to disappear...perhaps to return once again.

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Miss Juneteenth
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: The Never-Realm
description: The ninja arrive in the Never-Realm where they quickly find themselves overwhelmed. Luckily, they are taken in by a tribe of Ice Fishers who tell them Zane has been imprisoned by the evil Ice Emperor.

title: Bluebird
description: Steven questions the motives of a mysterious fusion that suddenly shows up at his house.

title: Volleyball
description: Steven is determined to help Pink Diamond's original Pearl heal the scar on her face.

title: La Batalla Decisiva
description: Luego de que la Célula Núcleo pusiera en estado de hibernación a los Bakugan de ambos equipos, Dan y Magnus se encuentran atrapados en una batalla donde lo apostarán todo.

title: An Unlikely Ally
description: Lloyd runs afoul of the Ice Emperor's Blizzard Samurai but is rescued by a strange wolf with whom an unlikely friendship develops.

title: Swampy Johnny
description: The Thundercats invite a super cool swamp man into the Cat's Lair who is on the run from some scary looking aliens!

title: Dia de Intercambio
description: Cuando los héroes creen que la vida del otro es más sencilla, intercambian sus papeles.

title: Fantasticos vs. AAAnimus Parte 2
description: Los Fantásticos unen fuerzas con Benton Dusk para rescatar a sus Bakugan y liberar la energía de la Célula Núcleo que AAAnimus tiene bajo su control.

title: La Leyenda del Torbaclaun
description: Cuando los Corazoncitos creen que el mítico Torbaclaun ha llegado al Valle Puro Corazón, Mao Mao intenta demostrarles que no es real.

title: Royal Flush
description: When the other kids fear Harold has accidentally flushed himself down Chef's fancy new toilet, they travel into the sewer on a rescue mission. But will they find Harold before the mythical Alligator King traps them underground forever?

title: Fantasticos vs. AAAnimus Parte 1
description: Los Fantásticos planean infiltrarse a AAAnimus para rescatar a sus Bakugan, pero Benton los detiene para ofrecerles un plan alternativo.

title: Free Perk
description: Robin teaches the Titans all about health insurance.

title: La Verdad Apesta
description: Colosal huele mal, pero Mao Mao y Adorabat no saben cómo decírselo.

title: Somewhere Over the Swingset
description: When the girls disobey the Professor and swing all the way over the swing set, they must deal with unexpected consequences.

title: El regreso de Thermometron 9000
description: Durante una ola de calor brutal, Axel y su equipo deben rastrear Thermometron 9000, robado por Ice Crusher para dos propósitos: ievitar que su pista de hockey se derrita y cebar los buenos juguetes en una revancha!

title: El Hada de los Gases
description: Después de perder su primer diente flojo por accidente y temer el no tener efectivo bajo la almohada, Leshawna intenta capturar al hada de los dientes. En vez de eso, captura al hada de los gases. Esto trae grandes consecuencias.

title: Let's Watch the Boxmore Show
description: Our heroes discover that the Boxmore security camera feed is the most entertaining thing ever.

title: Kiki's Pizza Delivery Service
description: Steven saves Kiki from some delicious nightmares.

title: Meet Panthro
description: Panthro may be the strongest cat on Third Earth, but one of his biggest strengths is that he can fix anything!  And the rest of the Thundercats break enough stuff to really put his skills to the test, but it's nothing a pro like Panthro can't handle.

title: La Leccion
description: Gumball y Darwin se hacen cargo de los trabajos de Larry durante 5 minutos y se dan cuenta de lo desagradable que son.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Apple's Formula
description: Apple needs to find a formula for comedy that will land him a movie role.

title: She Wore Red Velvet
description: When Booster and the JLA come under attack by a mysterious and unrelenting new villainess known as Red Velvet, Booster comes to realize she's actually the fiance he left at the altar in the future.

title: Carrie
description: Darwin sets out to find a photo of Carrie for the cover of the school yearbook - but they end up reminiscing about all their past spooky shenanigans. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Caillou Helps Out/Caillou the Firefighter/Caillou to the Rescue
description: Rosie is teething and just can't seem to fall asleep./The Fire chief visits Caillou's playschool to teach the children about fire drills./A mischievous Rosie hides Caillou's cars between the cushions on the sofa.

title: Scary Tales
description: During the gang's Halloween party, Unikitty discovers Brick isn't scared of anything! To get him in the holiday spirit, the gang tell their own ideas of what a spooky story is, hoping to scare the emotionless Rick for once, with each tale even scarier (and sillier) than the last!

title: Trading Day
description: When they think each others' lives are easier, the heroes switch roles.

title: Float On
description: Unikitty plans a parade to celebrate being unique, with everyone designing their own personalized floats! But Master Frown plans to ruin the parade with a super depressing float! It becomes an intense (and hilariously slow) car-versus-car float duel as Unikitty and the others try and take him down! Will Unikitty pump the brakes on Frown's low-speed scheme?

title: What's My Name? Starring Vambre and Prohyas Warrior!
description: The Warriors go to extreme measures so folks remember their names.

title: Unleashed
description: While the Justice League is away on a mission, Plastic Man is not only left in charge of the Watchtower, but also Superman's dog, Krypto.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Rivals
description: From Trigon to Terra to Darkseid, Robin counts down the worst of the worst: the greatest villains to ever challenge the Teen Titans!

title: Career Opportunities/Punch the Clock
description: Career Opportunities: After defeating Magnus the AO get an offer of employment from a surprising source Philomena Dusk!/Punch the Clock: During a commercial to celebrate their joining the AAAnimus team Dan and the AO rebel before they sellout.

title: Under the Overpass
description: Craig and his friends travel to find honeysuckle in the creek but discover a whole new part of the creek.

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Intergalactic Games
description: Super Hero High is facing off against Korugar Academy in the Intergalactic Games, but Lena Luthor takes advantage of the gathering of supers to enact her villainous plan.

title: Vulture's Nest
description: Craig and his friends start a band, but Craig is haunted by a frightening nightmare.

title: The Ultimate Adventure: Come Along with Me
description: The fate of Ooo is revealed to two adventurers in the distant future. Princess Bubblegum gathers her allies while Finn searches for a way to prevent the coming Great Gum War.

title: La Amiga
description: Anaís y Jamie forjan una extraña amistad cuando se las acusa de un crimen que no cometieron.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Dare Day
description: With Jeff on vacation, Sumo and Clarence egg each other on in a series of increasingly absurd and extreme dares. But will one of them put a stop to this dare day, before it goes too far?

title: Puedo Quedarmelo?
description: Tras toparse con una adorable criatura, híbrido de gato, perro y conejo, Ben no hace caso al consejo del abuelo Max y se lleva al animal a escondidas al Chatarra. Pero pronto empiezan los problemas porque ila creación del Dr. Animal lo delata!

title: Rooms
description: The Bears switch bedrooms for the night and get a glimpse of the living space of one of their brothers. But the deeper they go, hidden secrets are revealed.

title: Barehanded
description: When Green Lantern leaves his ring in an intergalactic restroom after washing his hands, he discovers it's gone, leading him on a wild chase for the aliens who might have taken it.

title: Selfish Shellfish
description: Apple and Onion are faced with a philosophical question: Are they truly doing good deeds for the good of other people or is it all just for them?

title: Can-Do Submarine Crew
description: Thomas and Percy think they're great communicators, but when they're tasked with delivering a submarine to Vicarstown, communication becomes a bit more difficult… to say the least!
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: #NoDerribenElArbol
description: Jessica Cruz y Pam Isley se unen para evitar que un antiguo árbol sea talado, pero ninguna se da cuenta de quien es el alter ego de la otra ni los extremos a los que llegarán para proteger lo que es importante.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Rey Koil
description: Ben y Gwen pasan el día como voluntarios en Repto Ranch y se enfrentan cara a cara con el Rey Koil. Pero necesitan superar rápidamente su miedo a las serpientes si quieren rescatar a las criaturas liberadas y derrotar al serpenteante villano.

title: Losing Ice
description: Feeling unappreciated, Ice Bear leaves his brothers to be the chef of a restaurant. Desperate to fill the void, Grizz and Panda look for Ice Bear's replacement.

title: Taz You Like It
description: Taz discovers pratfalls get him laughs and attention.

title: Ego - Egoista
description: Manzana y Cebolla tienen que demostrar que no son egoístas cuando hacen sus buenas acciones.

title: Un Nuevo Empleo
description: Durante un comercial para celebrar su contrato con el equipo AAAnimus, Dan y Los Fantásticos deciden rebelarse antes que traicionar sus principios.

title: Como Robots
description: Axel y el equipo se ven superados por Madcap cuando el malo usa sus dispositivos digitales para rastrear cada uno de sus movimientos en combate, lo que obliga a nuestros héroes a actuar de manera impredecible.

title: Un Aliado Peculiar
description: Lloyd se enfrenta a los Samurais Blizzard del Emperador de Hielo, pero es rescatado por un lobo extraño con quien desarrolla una amistad peculiar.

title: Caillou Goes Caroling/A Playschool Party/Caillou's Christmas Eve
description: Caillou goes out caroling for the very first time with Mommy, Daddy, Rosie, Grandpa and Grandma./It's a very special day at playschool as they celebrate the many ways of celebrating the holiday season./It's finally Christmas Eve and Caillou just can't wait for nighttime.

title: Developing Dilemna
description: Frankie lets Elliott get a pet, which doesn't go down well with their new neighbor.

title: Seed No Evil/City of Clipsville
description: Seed No Evil: When a prehistoric caveman thaws out in Townsville, the girls must stop him from stealing the Mayor's seeds./City of Clipsville: The girls reminisce on their adventures in these new, never-before-seen clips!

title: Drawn to Making it Happen with Sidney Keys
description: Cartoon Network celebrates Black History Month with Sidney Keys III, a 15-year-old rising entrepreneur and the founder and CEO of "Books n Bros," an African American literature book club for male youth ages 7-13 years old. Focused on promoting literacy among young Black boys and introducing them to positive representation in literature, Keys' advocacy is paving the way for change by creating a place for boys to be mentored by their "Big Bros" and connect over a shared love for reading.

title: The One
description: Gumball and Darwin are joking around, but when Tobias joins in and makes fun of Gumball, he's incredibly offended. They explain to Tobias that to make those jokes he'd need to be higher on Gumball's friend list. They think that's the end of it, but Tobias is after that number one spot.

title: Wackily Ever After
description: Pocoyo and his friends are playing dressing up and the narrator decides to tell a story. The traditional fairy tale takes on a decidedly wacky hue as the characters all undercut the conventions with hilarious and surprising results.

title: The Invitation
description: Craig and his friends are invited to an exclusive tea party with delicious desserts, if they can last to the end of the party.

title: Of Predators and Prey Part 1
description: After a heated argument, Ben and Rook go their separate ways, giving Khyber the Huntsman his best chance to capture Ben! (Introducing Dr. Psychobos, new Nemetrix aliens Mucillator & Terroranchula; new Ben alien Ballweevil.)

title: Drawn to Community
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating awesome kids who are giving back and making a difference to those around them. CN is recognizing extraordinary girls who are channeling their interests into outreach as they are Drawn to… Community!

title: Compost to Go
description: When Mush-Mush, Chep and Lilit take their compost meals back to their home-tree to eat, they think they have made a great new discovery - compost to go! They set up a delivery service so everyone can eat at home too. It's so cool! Except Sushi-Mushi misses hosting everyone at the Food Snail, and everyone starts missing eating together.

title: Wicked Shades
description: When Pizza Steve borrows Uncle Grandpa's sunglasses, he sees things in a whole new light.

title: Que Vengan Los Chicos Malos
description: Axel, Zoe y el equipo se enfrentan a Madcap y sus secuaces mientras aterrorizan a un supermercado local.

title: The Master
description: Dad decides to resolve the Watterson family's differences through the power and magic of his favorite roleplaying game. As they embark on the adventure of a lifetime and battle mythical creatures, will they finally manage to put their differences aside and work together?
